content: ['view', 'pure', 'View', 'Pure', '// SPDX-License-Identifier: MITpragma solidity ^0.8.17;contract ViewAndPure {    uint public x = 1;    // Promise not to modify the state.    function addToX(uint y) public view returns (uint) {        return x + y;    }    // Promise not to modify or read from the state.    function add(uint i, uint j) public pure returns (uint) {        return i + j;    }}']
